      "comment": "SANTORINI BALE (1) well back settling but did wind up strongly to finish 4th and beaten only 5 lengths (23.53) at Warragul. Key runner on her best form. INTEX BALE (8) was safely held in tougher company last start after settling well back at Ballarat, but prior to that won by 1.1 lengths at this track (23.15) beating SOLAR TOBY in a Grade 5 on April 7. Better than last start and can bounce back. BARRY BALE (2) turned in a modest effort most recently when sixth at this track over 400m behind Magpie Harry (23.96) in a Grade 5. The form out of his last race has been franked. Can do much better this time. SOLAR TOBY (3) has strong claims after a top-three finish last time out.",
